OL,3,CRail passengers urged to plan ahead
OL,4,Cafter heavy rain arrives in Scotland
OL,6,FRail passengers have been urged to
OL,7,Fplan ahead and allow extra time for
OL,8,Fjourneys as heavy rain causes
OL,9,Fdisruption to train services.
OL,11,FThe Met Office has issued a yellow
OL,12,Fweather warning for heavy and
OL,13,Fpersistent rain, with up to 60mm
OL,14,Fexpected to fall between Monday
OL,15,Fevening and 18:00 tonight (Tuesday 9
OL,16,FApril).
OL,18,FSpeed restrictions will be in place
OL,19,Falong some sections of routes between
OL,20,FGlasgow to Carlisle and Edinburgh to
OL,21,FBerwick.
