OL,3,CRail passengers urged to plan ahead
OL,4,Cafter heavy rain arrives in Scotland
OL,6,FLiam Sumpter, route director at
OL,7,FNetwork Rail Scotland, said: "Speed
OL,8,Frestrictions are being introduced as
OL,9,Fthe rain moves in because we know that
OL,10,Fslowing trains down reduces the
OL,11,Fchances of striking obstructions on
OL,12,Fthe line.
OL,14,F"Our engineering teams will respond to
OL,15,Fany issues on the railway while our
OL,16,Fcontrol room will monitor the weather
OL,17,Fthroughout the day.
